lowed Up by the Dark Atlantic |url=https://www.newspapers.com/image/335370557/ |work=The Tampa Tribune |date=28 Sep 1980}}</ref> <ref name=Kaye-1995>{{cite news |last1=Kaye |first1=Ken |title=50 years after the Lost Patrol: vanishing of 27 still a mystery |url=https://www.newspapers.com/image/238669966/ |accessdate=26 September 2018 |work=South Florida Sun Sentinel |date=3 Dec 1995}}</ref> <ref name=Kusche-2015>{{cite journal |last1=Kushce |first1=Larry |title=The Bermuda Triangle Mystery Delusion: Looking Back after Forty Years |journal=Skeptical Inquirer |date=Nov–Dec 2015 |volume=39.6 |url=https://www.csicop.org/si/show/the_bermuda_triangle_mystery_delusion |accessdate=3 October 2018}}</ref> <ref name=CSI>[[Committee for Skeptical Inquiry|CSI's]] [http://www.csicop.org/about/csi_fellows_and_staff/ List of Fellows] listed as Lawrence Kusche.</ref> <ref name=Upton-1977>{{cite news |last1=Upton |first1=Kim |title=A Penchant for Popcorn |url=https://www.newspapers.com/image/262240979/ |accessdate=25 September 2018 |work=The Honolulu Advertiser |date=6 Nov 1977}}</ref> }}
